  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/9f07b19c4e4e3d982ad10a865decc972.webp?t=1721214305\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in the renewed terror of Echoes of Madness, where every shadow and whisper hides unimaginable secrets. Eighty years after the inauguration of the Greenview Psychiatric Hospital, Alex Turner, a private investigator turned head of security, faces the horrors that lurk in this unsettling sanatorium. Hired by a mysterious benefactor, Alex must unravel the truth behind the disappearances and deaths that plague the place. What he discovers is just the tip of the iceberg in a chilling story that intertwines life and death.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/d030023795b55263c71b811e017987b1.avif?t=1721214305\" width=600 height=88 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/43b4b9af9e0631365fb91aeeb9a447d6.webp?t=1721214305\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Delve into the disturbed mind of Greenview and uncover the darkest secrets hidden behind its walls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/5ffebf2fa5e7958d4219252679412a34.poster.avif?t=1721214305\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/5ffebf2fa5e7958d4219252679412a34.webm?t=1721214305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/5ffebf2fa5e7958d4219252679412a34.mp4?t=1721214305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/1f9e4d3e056b1e8eb05e9965b8d646de.webp?t=1721214305\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Monitor the cameras, observe anomalies, manage the center's staff, and maintain control of vital systems, both of the sanatorium and yourself.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/631b98ab75381de8ab777dcf9f64cfaa.poster.avif?t=1721214305\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/631b98ab75381de8ab777dcf9f64cfaa.webm?t=1721214305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/631b98ab75381de8ab777dcf9f64cfaa.mp4?t=1721214305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/0ebad500cd10308f54a306bfb576726f.webp?t=1721214305\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Enjoy a sound and visual environment that will make you feel every shiver. Experience an oppressive and realistic atmosphere that will completely immerse you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/f760868e0b5a8ef745c2fb63f492fcc2.poster.avif?t=1721214305\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/f760868e0b5a8ef745c2fb63f492fcc2.webm?t=1721214305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/f760868e0b5a8ef745c2fb63f492fcc2.mp4?t=1721214305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/5b672ab8f608b6ba77d1378d120b37b9.webp?t=1721214305\" width=600 height=30 /></span><br>Get caught up in a narrative that will push you to the edge of your fears and challenge your sanity.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/e65cc32513d3e4794aef0c49da4db1c9.poster.avif?t=1721214305\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/e65cc32513d3e4794aef0c49da4db1c9.webm?t=1721214305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2603260/extras/e65cc32513d3e4794aef0c49da4db1c9.mp4?t=1721214305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready to face your worst nightmares? Echoes of Madness awaits you at Greenview. Surviving your watch is just the beginning.",
